{"tid":1932663,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"英國增至逾2600宗新冠肺炎　大部分學校當地周五下午起關閉","createTime":"2020-03-19T00:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T00:48:05.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb9c13813e94bddc873f8805a9c21e799f67eb4","tid":1932663,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"英國單日新增逾700宗新冠肺炎個案，累計逾2600宗，增至104人死亡。首相約翰遜宣布，大部分學校當地周五下午起關閉，直至另行通知；而一名曾到訪首相府的學者，因為有高燒等徵狀，正自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦帝國學院數理生物學教授弗格森，周一曾到唐寧街首相府，希望說服政府加強應對疫情。他在社交網站表示，周二有乾咳後決定自我隔離，於周三發高燒。暫時未知弗格森曾否與首相約翰遜見面，首相發言人表示，約翰遜並沒有病徵。<br />\n<br />\n弗格森在研究中，比較1918年的流感疫情，指出如果完全不採取任何措施，最終英國可能有超過50萬人死於新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5e728c96335d1920243740ac/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE2600%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E8%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5e728c96335d1920243740ac%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%2580%25BE2600%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=15866b6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5e728c96335d1920243740ac/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE2600%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E8%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89</a>"},{"pid":"376c388a3f2fe9be1e9cdb5bf149c0040ceaa63f","tid":1932663,"uid":107842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"唔要tvb<br />\n<br />\n汁：<br />\n<a h